-# Verticals v3
+# Shorts — AI YouTube Shorts Pipeline
 
-AI-native vertical video engine: topic + niche -> research -> script -> visuals -> voice -> captions -> music -> thumbnail -> upload.
+토픽 + 니치 → 리서치 → 스크립트 → 비주얼 → 보이스 → 캡션 → 음악 → 조립 → 업로드
+
+Based on [Verticals v3](https://github.com/rushindrasinha/youtube-shorts-pipeline)
+
+## Architecture
+
+```
+Topic ──► Research (DuckDuckGo)
+              │
+              ▼
+          Script (Claude/Gemini/GPT/Ollama)
+              │
+              ▼
+          B-roll (Gemini Imagen / Pexels / ComfyUI)
+              │
+              ▼
+          Voice (Edge TTS / ElevenLabs / Kokoro)
+              │
+              ▼
+          Captions (Whisper → ASS + SRT)
+              │
+              ▼
+          Music (royalty-free + voice ducking)
+              │
+              ▼
+          Assemble (ffmpeg → 9:16 MP4)
+              │
+              ▼
+          Upload (YouTube / TikTok / Reels)
+```
+
+## Quick Start
+
+```bash
+# 래퍼 스크립트 사용
+~/2lab.ai/skills/shorts/scripts/run.sh run --news "Elon Musk launches new AI" --niche tech --lang en
+
+# 또는 직접 실행
+cd ~/2lab.ai/skills/shorts
+.venv/bin/python -m verticals run --news "headline" --niche tech
+
+# 드래프트만 (영상 생성 없이 스크립트만)
+.venv/bin/python -m verticals draft --news "headline" --niche tech
+
+# 트렌딩 토픽 검색
+.venv/bin/python -m verticals topics --niche tech --limit 10
+
+# 니치 목록 보기
+.venv/bin/python -m verticals niches
+```
 
 ## Commands
 
+| Command | Description |
+|---------|-------------|
+| `run` | 풀 파이프라인: draft → produce → upload |
+| `draft` | 스크립트 + 메타데이터 생성만 |
+| `produce` | 드래프트 → 영상 생성 |
+| `upload` | 영상 → YouTube 업로드 |
+| `topics` | 트렌딩 토픽 검색 |
+| `niches` | 사용 가능한 니치 프로필 목록 |
+
+## Key Flags
+
+| Flag | Options | Default |
+|------|---------|---------|
+| `--niche` | tech, gaming, finance, fitness, cooking, travel, etc. | general |
+| `--provider` | claude, gemini, openai, ollama | claude |
+| `--voice` | edge, elevenlabs, say, kokoro | edge |
+| `--platform` | shorts, reels, tiktok, all | shorts |
+| `--lang` | en, ko, ja, hi, es, pt, de, fr | en |
+| `--dry-run` | 드래프트만 생성 | - |
+| `--discover` | 트렌딩 토픽 자동 검색 | - |
+| `--auto-pick` | LLM이 최적 토픽 선택 | - |
+
+## Available Niches (16+)
+
+tech, gaming, finance, fitness, cooking, travel, true_crime, science, politics, entertainment, sports, fashion, education, motivation, comedy, general, **textcard** (1:1 정사각형)
+
