+## Troubleshooting
 
-Docs: https://github.com/rushindrasinha/verticals
-Product: https://verticals.gg
+| Error | Solution |
+|-------|----------|
+| No Claude access | `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` 설정 또는 `claude` CLI 설치 |
+| ffmpeg not found | `apt install ffmpeg` 또는 빌드 |
+| Whisper OOM | 작은 모델 사용: `--whisper-model base` |
+| YouTube upload fail | `python3 scripts/setup_youtube_oauth.py` 실행 |
